    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📧 Email Validation (Batch)\n\n**Purpose**\nVerifies that emails in `cleaned_leads` are real and can actually receive mail. Prevents bounced emails and protects sender reputation during outreach.\n\n**How it works**\nRuns every **5 hours** → picks 10 leads with unverified emails → checks each one via AbstractAPI → updates `email_valid` and `email_verification_status` in the database.\n\n**Key Rules**\n- Only processes **10 emails per run** to respect API limits\n- Sets status to `DELIVERABLE`, `UNDELIVERABLE`, or `unknown`\n- Disposable emails are marked as invalid",
        "height": 544,
